                "sheet_id": 15612086,
                "entry_type_id": 19,
                "label": "-Conduct a Daily Tailgate Safety Meeting with site personel prior to commencing\ndaily activities. Safety topics can be selected from the attached table.\n-Address potential hazards and controls for tasks that will be conducted\n-Discuss air monitoring, training, PPE and other appropriate requirments.\n-Follow-up on noted items and document the resolution of any action items.\n",
