                "id": 119364212,
                "type": "entry",
                "form_id": 1448271,
                "sheet_id": 15612086,
                "entry_type_id": 19,
                "label": "1. Accident Reporting\n2. Air Monitoring\n3. Air Monitoring and Action Levels\n4. Alcohol Consumption and Worksite Safety\n5. Cold Stress\n6. Confined Space Entry\n7. Crane Safety\n8. Daily Work Task Hazards\n9. Decontamination\n10. Disciplinary Policy for Not Following Safety Rules/Safe Work Practices\n11. Drill Rig Safety\n12. Electrical Safety\n13. Emergency Response\n14. Ergonomics\n15. Excavation Trenching Hazards\n16. Eye Wash Sation Location\n17. Fall Protection\n18. Fire Safety/Bonding-Grounding Techniques\n19. First Aid/CPR\n20. Fugitive Dust Control\n21.General Site Safety Hazards\n22.Hand Tool Hazards\n23. Hazard Communication/Location of MSDS/Review of HAZMAT Properties\n24. Health and Safety Plan\n25. Hearing Protection\n26. Heat Stress\n27. Heavy Machinery\n28. Hospital Directions\n29. Housekeeping\n30.Material Handling\n31.Mechanical Hazards/Guarding/LOTO\n32. Overhead Hazards\n33. Personal Protective Equipment (PPE)\n34.Respiratory Protection and Filter Change-Out Schedule\n35. Roles and Responsibilities\n36. Site Security\n37. Smoking and Break Areas\n38. Tank Removal Safety\n39. Underground Utilities\n40. Use of \"Buddy System\"\n41. Vapor Control\n42. Water Hazards\n43. Welding Safety\n44. Work Stoppage",
